{"tid":2356473,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"局長不滿「安心出行」下載數字   希望能有更多市民使用","createTime":"2021-01-06T22:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T02:04:53.000Z","uid":45133,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb61b24494951d9ab683e90918644cf6a1a82736","tid":2356473,"uid":45133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:57:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://video-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t42.9040-2/126277240_2823850041186409_8420197133526840845_n.mp4?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=985c63&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImxlZ2FjeV9zZCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=OJQwMhsueXsAX-vTAzP&amp;rl=351&amp;vabr=195&amp;_nc_ht=video-syd2-1.xx&amp;oh=f636d5f943d14d86907796b7c1e175de&amp;oe=5FF667F1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft42.9040-2%2F126277240_2823850041186409_8420197133526840845_n.mp4%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D985c63%26efg%3DeyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImxlZ2FjeV9zZCJ9%26_nc_ohc%3DOJQwMhsueXsAX-vTAzP%26rl%3D351%26vabr%3D195%26_nc_ht%3Dvideo-syd2-1.xx%26oh%3Df636d5f943d14d86907796b7c1e175de%26oe%3D5FF667F1&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5obCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=de229da8\" target=\"_blank\">https://video-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t42.9040-2/126277240_2823850041186409_8420197133526840845_n.mp4?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=985c63&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImxlZ2FjeV9zZCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=OJQwMhsueXsAX-vTAzP&amp;rl=351&amp;vabr=195&amp;_nc_ht=video-syd2-1.xx&amp;oh=f636d5f943d14d86907796b7c1e175de&amp;oe=5FF667F1</a><br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局長薛永恒今日（6 日）在立法會會議上表示，「安心出行」App 下載數字並不令人滿意，惟強調現階段仍是自願參與，但不會排除強制要求市民下載的可能性。另外，他提到未來將推出「電子針檢卡」，並會積極研究將相關功能加入「安心出行」App 。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前強制食肆與表列所處需要申請「安心出行」QR Code，目前已有 6.7 萬個場所已貼出二維碼，而創新及科技局長薛永恒今日（6 日）在立法會例行會議上透露，「安心出行」App 至今有 43 萬下載人次，表示此數字並不令人滿意，並寄望可有更多市民下載使用，但強調現階段仍是自願參與，惟不會排除強制市民使用 App 的可能性。<br />\n <br />\n另外，薛永恒表示目前正研發接種疫苗的預約系統，並將於本月推出「電子針檢卡」，方便市民記錄接種疫苗的時間與次數，而「電子針檢卡」亦將用於記錄病毒檢測結果。民建聯梁志祥建議，當局可將「電子針檢卡」加入安心出行」App ，薛永恒回應指會積極研究如何在合併後，仍能發揮兩者功能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，個大陸喱徐教授講嘢聽撚到我燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係你講撚哂英文啦，唔知你up乜鳩"},{"pid":"45e568664b329782d07034950253b6915123b18a","tid":2356473,"uid":65289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:18:17.000Z","msg":"好似保險佬捽數咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a984ac9eb2b8748892a6274e02554aab1972068","tid":2356473,"uid":55011,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:29:27.000Z","msg":"一個人派十部電話 每個人都要下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b262906d29018dfd2ff79fd88d817b084daa7c2","tid":2356473,"uid":22088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45e568664b329782d07034950253b6915123b18a","tid":2356473,"uid":65289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:18:17.000Z","msg":"好似保險佬捽數咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:49:20.000Z","msg":"一直以黎都係 大愚過唔到 現家咪用疫症做利益輸送kpi"},{"pid":"0e9343f9634ac4e5dc8bff8a9e35980dca13d367","tid":2356473,"uid":76587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:52:39.000Z","msg":"佢自己都唔會嘟 走嚟叫我嘟 on9"},{"pid":"67bd4b6fe4b208e520e20b5fa4dec1506fac6b93","tid":2356473,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:53:17.000Z","msg":"係得香港班狗官咁大口氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c1c8d86ad76549e539df46bb414e1ffd62299b","tid":2356473,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:55:56.000Z","msg":"你派部iphone俾我我考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c7202f8f